data.description: Get ready to be amazed with this gem nestled in the Greene Croft neighborhood of Mooresville with its BRAND NEW MODERN DECK, solar panels 2024, new A/C & Furnace 2022, Water Heater 2023, Garage Door Opener 2023, new front door, smart door locks & switches, Ring door bell and floodlight cameras, new toilets, fresh coat of paint in the lower level (Living room, dining room, kitchen, laundry room, and ½ bathroom) and new wood stair risers. Loft area offers addt'l living space, perfect for use as a home office/media room. Open concept kitchen tastefully updated to include high-end appliances including a gas stove. Retreat to the generously sized bedrooms, including a huge primary suite with its ensuite bathroom & over sized walk-in closet. One of the bedrooms is perfectly suited to serve as a secondary main bedroom, offering flexibility & comfort for multi-generational living/guest accommodations.  This is the one you've been looking for and its waiting for you!
